uk.gov.gchq.gaffer.analytic.operation

Class MetaData

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.gov.gchq.gaffer.analytic.operation.MetaData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class MetaData
extends Object
implements Serializable
    MetaData contains information relating to how the analytic is to be displayed in the Analytic UI. It contains the icon, which should be in an SVG string format, and the colour of the analytic card shown on the Analytic UI. The default visualisation type is table and currently is the only one supported by the Analytic UI.
